  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Electrical Panel Assembler",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position: Electrical Panel Assembler!</strong></p>\n<p>We are looking for a dedicated and skilled individual to join our customer’s production team. In this role, you will be responsible for assembling electrical panels, installing components, and ensuring high-quality workmanship in a safe and efficient manner.</p>\n<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>Perform assembly work on electrical panels.</p>\n<p>Install electrical components and run cables according to specifications.</p>\n<p>Maintain 5S standards on the production floor and ensure daily working tools are in good condition.</p>\n<p>Carry out other duties as assigned by the superior.</p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ability to read and interpret single-line diagrams.</li>\n  <li>Self-disciplined and able to work independently.</li>\n  <li>Strong teamwork skills with a high level of commitment.</li>\n  <li>Willing to cooperate with overtime arrangements.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Overtime allowance (including weekend OT)</li>\n  <li>Transport allowance</li>\n  <li>Attendance incentive</li>\n  <li>Lunch subsidy</li>\n  <li>Weekday transport provided</li>\n  <li>Annual Wage Supplement (AWS) and Variable Bonus (VB)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Location: Tuas</p>\n<p>Working Hours: Mon to Fri 8:15am to 5:45pm </p>\n<p>Expereince: Fitter - no need experience; Electrician - 1 year</p>\n<p>Techskills Career Services (S) Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA)</p>\n<p>What’s app your profile to +65 86701803 or email to sheela@techskills.com.sg </p>\n<p>Thank you </p>\n<p>Techskills Career Services (S) Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA. R23113418</p>\n<p><br></p>",
